.modal-headermessage
  .modal-title
    .h4.text-info {{DownloadResume.offer.name}}
      span.font-bold.m-l-xs {{DownloadResume.offer.price}}
      .close(ng-click='DownloadResume.cancel()') Ã—
.modal-body
  p {{DownloadResume.offer.innerDescription}}
  .radio(ng-if="DownloadResume.value === 'return'")
    label.i-checks
      input(type='radio', name='a', value='return_pickup', checked='', ng-model="DownloadResume.data.return_pickup")
      i
      | The sender will pick-up the package directly from Shoppre facility.
      | You shall pay them for the charges, if any.
  textarea.form-control(rows=4, ng-if="DownloadResume.value === 'return'",  ng-model="DownloadResume.data.message1")
  .radio(ng-if="DownloadResume.value === 'return'")
    label.i-checks
      input(type='radio', name='a', value='return_shoppre', checked='', ng-model="DownloadResume.data.return_shoppre")
      i
      | Shoppre has to return the package for you to the Sender.
      | You will be charged as per our Domestic Shipping Rates which will be notified to you via email.
  textarea.form-control(rows=4, ng-hide="DownloadResume.value === 'abandon'",  ng-model="DownloadResume.data.message2")
  .checkbox(ng-hide="DownloadResume.value === 'abandon'")
    label.i-checks
      input(type='checkbox', value='')
      i
      | I understand that I will have to pay a fee of INR 400 for the return, which will appear in my Shoppre Wallet.
.modal-footer
  a.btn.btn-warning.text-u-c(ng-click='DownloadResume.cancel()') Cancel Request
  a.btn.btn-success.text-u-c(ng-click='DownloadResume.submitRequest()') Submit Request
